name: No. 7 Repel Essential Oil
description:
No. 7 Repel Essential Oil, 10 ml

Ingredients: Eucalyptus Globulus, Cedarwood Virginiana and Geranium. Blended in pure Jojoba Oil.

How to Use: Blended to apply directly to skin since it is suspended in Jojoba oil.  Simply apply a thin layer repeatedly on skin that is exposed to biting insects.
